{
  "font_size": 0.4,
  "font_color": "#FFFFFF",
  "background_alpha": 0.5,
  "background_color": "#9C27B0",
  "Stroke": "none",
  "type": "AIsubtitle",
  "lang": "zh",
  "version": "eng-1.2.0-Index-johns-pen-lite",
  "body": [
    {
      "content": "在本节课中",
      "from": 0.22,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 1,
      "to": 1.22
    },
    {
      "content": "我们将讲解知识图谱的概念",
      "from": 1.22,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 2,
      "to": 3.36
    },
    {
      "content": "以及它们如何帮助表示和检索数据中的关系",
      "from": 3.36,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 3,
      "to": 7.14
    },
    {
      "content": "接下来你将探索数据集",
      "from": 7.14,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 4,
      "to": 8.78
    },
    {
      "content": "你将动手构建一个知识图谱",
      "from": 8.78,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 5,
      "to": 11.04
    },
    {
      "content": "让我们开始吧",
      "from": 11.04,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 6,
      "to": 12.52
    },
    {
      "content": "那么什么是知识图谱",
      "from": 12.52,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 7,
      "to": 14.48
    },
    {
      "content": "我们暂时退后一步，回顾关系型数据库",
      "from": 14.48,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 8,
      "to": 19.73
    },
    {
      "content": "以及关系型模式的结构",
      "from": 19.73,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 9,
      "to": 21.79
    },
    {
      "content": "我们可能都熟悉这样的场景",
      "from": 21.79,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 10,
      "to": 24.759
    },
    {
      "content": "左边有一个表格，右边也有一个表格",
      "from": 24.759,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 11,
      "to": 28.38
    },
    {
      "content": "中间这个表格",
      "from": 28.38,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 12,
      "to": 29.66
    },
    {
      "content": "这是连接表，允许人员与产品之间建立多对多关系",
      "from": 29.66,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 13,
      "to": 34.5
    },
    {
      "content": "在本例中",
      "from": 34.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 14,
      "to": 36.41
    },
    {
      "content": "让我们考虑这两个表格和连接表",
      "from": 36.41,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 15,
      "to": 38.61
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你提出一个问题",
      "from": 39.73,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 16,
      "to": 40.57
    },
    {
      "content": "比如这个人购买了哪些产品",
      "from": 40.57,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 17,
      "to": 43.69
    },
    {
      "content": "你会先从人员表开始，选择此处的人员",
      "from": 43.69,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 18,
      "to": 46.85
    },
    {
      "content": "其标识为abk",
      "from": 46.85,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 19,
      "to": 49.01
    },
    {
      "content": "当然你需要通过连接到人员产品表",
      "from": 49.01,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 20,
      "to": 52.34
    },
    {
      "content": "你会看到人员产品表中存在abk与某把椅子的关联",
      "from": 52.34,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 21,
      "to": 57.36
    },
    {
      "content": "a k与一盏台灯",
      "from": 57.36,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 22,
      "to": 58.3
    },
    {
      "content": "abk与一张书桌",
      "from": 58.3,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 23,
      "to": 59.82
    },
    {
      "content": "太棒了，一个词",
      "from": 59.82,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 24,
      "to": 61.96
    },
    {
      "content": "从人员表跨连接到人员产品表再到产品表",
      "from": 61.96,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 25,
      "to": 66.08
    },
    {
      "content": "现在你已得到完整答案",
      "from": 66.08,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 26,
      "to": 67.74
    },
    {
      "content": "从abk可以看到这里是他购买的产品，包括椅子",
      "from": 67.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 27,
      "to": 72.84
    },
    {
      "content": "台灯和书桌",
      "from": 72.84,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 28,
      "to": 73.64
    },
    {
      "content": "你可以获取这些购买的详细信息",
      "from": 73.64,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 29,
      "to": 76.36
    },
    {
      "content": "如果扩展这个问题",
      "from": 76.36,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 30,
      "to": 78.2
    },
    {
      "content": "并询问还有谁购买了abk购买的产品",
      "from": 78.2,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 31,
      "to": 82.66
    },
    {
      "content": "你从相同的连接开始",
      "from": 82.66,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 32,
      "to": 83.86
    },
    {
      "content": "从abk到产品",
      "from": 83.86,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 33,
      "to": 85.62
    },
    {
      "content": "然后连接回人员产品表",
      "from": 85.62,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 34,
      "to": 88.54
    },
    {
      "content": "再从那里回到人员表",
      "from": 88.54,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 35,
      "to": 90.96
    },
    {
      "content": "现在你会得到购买了abk同类产品的人员ee",
      "from": 90.96,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 36,
      "to": 96.969
    },
    {
      "content": "但注意ee还多买了一个产品",
      "from": 96.969,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 37,
      "to": 100.469
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "from": 100.469,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 38,
      "to": 101.27
    },
    {
      "content": "这很有趣",
      "from": 101.27,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 39,
      "to": 102.85
    },
    {
      "content": "因此我们可以进一步扩展这个问题",
      "from": 103.05,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 40,
      "to": 107.35
    },
    {
      "content": "哪种产品",
      "from": 107.35,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 41,
      "to": 108.19
    },
    {
      "content": "我们应该推荐abk下次购买",
      "from": 108.19,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 42,
      "to": 111.02
    },
    {
      "content": "这就是推荐查询的基础",
      "from": 111.02,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 43,
      "to": 114.3
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你发现abk的购买模式",
      "from": 114.3,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 44,
      "to": 117.42
    },
    {
      "content": "与其他人或群体的购买模式匹配",
      "from": 117.42,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 45,
      "to": 121.87
    },
    {
      "content": "想要推荐给abk的是其他人购买的产品",
      "from": 121.87,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 46,
      "to": 125.73
    },
    {
      "content": "而abk尚未购买的，因此同样的连接步骤",
      "from": 125.73,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 47,
      "to": 128.77
    },
    {
      "content": "从abk通过产品连接到购买同类产品的其他人员",
      "from": 128.77,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 48,
      "to": 133.87
    },
    {
      "content": "连接次数太多",
      "from": 133.87,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 49,
      "to": 135.6
    },
    {
      "content": "这有点复杂",
      "from": 135.6,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 50,
      "to": 137.51
    },
    {
      "content": "其实有一个更优雅的方式来思考这个问题",
      "from": 137.51,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 51,
      "to": 139.83
    },
    {
      "content": "现在来执行这个查询",
      "from": 139.83,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 52,
      "to": 141.05
    },
    {
      "content": "让我们将其转换为图形结构",
      "from": 141.05,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 53,
      "to": 142.97
    },
    {
      "content": "第一步是删除所有无关记录",
      "from": 142.97,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 54,
      "to": 146.679
    },
    {
      "content": "所有那些未参与原始查询的优质记录",
      "from": 146.679,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 55,
      "to": 149.269
    },
    {
      "content": "暂时将这些记录搁置一旁，专注于已知记录",
      "from": 149.269,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 56,
      "to": 152.629
    },
    {
      "content": "属于数据集的部分",
      "from": 152.629,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 57,
      "to": 154.069
    },
    {
      "content": "到目前为止",
      "from": 154.069,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 58,
      "to": 154.509
    },
    {
      "content": "这对推荐给abk的内容查询至关重要",
      "from": 154.509,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 59,
      "to": 158.6
    },
    {
      "content": "移除中间所有联合表记录",
      "from": 158.6,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 60,
      "to": 161.2
    },
    {
      "content": "将这些转换为箭头",
      "from": 161.2,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 61,
      "to": 162.1
    },
    {
      "content": "直接连接abk到他购买的产品",
      "from": 162.1,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 62,
      "to": 165.69
    },
    {
      "content": "同样处理ee到他们购买的产品",
      "from": 165.69,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 63,
      "to": 169.2
    },
    {
      "content": "现在稍微调整记录位置",
      "from": 169.2,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 64,
      "to": 171.6
    },
    {
      "content": "这样abk在一边，另一边",
      "from": 171.6,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 65,
      "to": 175.17
    },
    {
      "content": "现在看起来整洁多了",
      "from": 175.17,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 66,
      "to": 176.81
    },
    {
      "content": "更容易理解其中逻辑",
      "from": 176.81,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 67,
      "to": 178.55
    },
    {
      "content": "a k和e都连接到中间产品",
      "from": 178.55,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 68,
      "to": 182.06
    },
    {
      "content": "但此人还连接到与abk无关的另一产品",
      "from": 182.06,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 69,
      "to": 188.32
    },
    {
      "content": "可以通过模式匹配将其转化为查询",
      "from": 188.32,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 70,
      "to": 192.96
    },
    {
      "content": "以abk在左侧开始",
      "from": 192.96,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 71,
      "to": 195.329
    },
    {
      "content": "可以用名为cipher的查询语言描述",
      "from": 195.329,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 72,
      "to": 199.109
    },
    {
      "content": "看起来类似sql",
      "from": 199.109,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 73,
      "to": 201.429
    },
    {
      "content": "如果sql具备模式匹配能力",
      "from": 201.429,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 74,
      "to": 203.94
    },
    {
      "content": "这里描述要查找的数据记录模式",
      "from": 203.94,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 75,
      "to": 208.879
    },
    {
      "content": "从我们将称为abk的数据记录开始",
      "from": 208.879,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 76,
      "to": 212.339
    },
    {
      "content": "具有person标签",
      "from": 212.339,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 77,
      "to": 214.47
    },
    {
      "content": "并有一个名为key的属性",
      "from": 214.47,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 78,
      "to": 217.09
    },
    {
      "content": "其值为abk",
      "from": 217.09,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 79,
      "to": 218.95
    },
    {
      "content": "这部分用圆括号表示",
      "from": 218.95,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 80,
      "to": 220.49
    },
    {
      "content": "在图论中这是一个节点",
      "from": 220.49,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 81,
      "to": 222.84
    },
    {
      "content": "然后有一个右向箭头带purchased",
      "from": 222.84,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 82,
      "to": 228.08
    },
    {
      "content": "这是关系类型",
      "from": 228.08,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 83,
      "to": 229.54
    },
    {
      "content": "即为购买行为",
      "from": 229.54,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 84,
      "to": 230.73
    },
    {
      "content": "匹配abk购买到其他括号中的模式",
      "from": 230.73,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 85,
      "to": 235.63
    },
    {
      "content": "我们称之为abk产品",
      "from": 235.63,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 86,
      "to": 237.66
    },
    {
      "content": "从abk到匹配产品的模式",
      "from": 237.66,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 87,
      "to": 241.76
    },
    {
      "content": "可以直接返回这些结果",
      "from": 241.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 88,
      "to": 243.699
    },
    {
      "content": "对应中间部分",
      "from": 243.699,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 89,
      "to": 246.45
    },
    {
      "content": "可扩展该模式包含其他购买者",
      "from": 246.53,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 90,
      "to": 251.5
    },
    {
      "content": "从abk到其购买产品",
      "from": 251.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 91,
      "to": 254.5
    },
    {
      "content": "还可关联到产品并说明",
      "from": 254.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 92,
      "to": 258.76
    },
    {
      "content": "有其他人购买了这些产品",
      "from": 258.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 93,
      "to": 260.84
    },
    {
      "content": "该模式会找到与abk共有的产品",
      "from": 260.84,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 94,
      "to": 265.61
    },
    {
      "content": "可进一步扩展以解决推荐问题",
      "from": 265.61,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 95,
      "to": 270.2
    },
    {
      "content": "而不仅仅是寻找其他产品",
      "from": 270.2,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 96,
      "to": 272.8
    },
    {
      "content": "其他产品具有独特属性",
      "from": 273.84,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 97,
      "to": 275.4
    },
    {
      "content": "这些是abk尚未拥有的",
      "from": 275.4,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 98,
      "to": 278.76
    },
    {
      "content": "保持相同模式从abk到产品再到他人",
      "from": 278.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 99,
      "to": 283.33
    },
    {
      "content": "并扩展到其他产品",
      "from": 283.33,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 100,
      "to": 285.89
    },
    {
      "content": "现在我们添加了一个谓词，表示我们实际上希望一个负模式为真",
      "from": 285.89,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 101,
      "to": 290.719
    },
    {
      "content": "Abk 没有购买那些其他产品",
      "from": 290.719,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 102,
      "to": 293.99
    },
    {
      "content": "所以Abk 没有购买那些其他产品的地方",
      "from": 293.99,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 103,
      "to": 296.85
    },
    {
      "content": "所以下方那个虚线部分",
      "from": 296.85,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 104,
      "to": 299.47
    },
    {
      "content": "从Abk 到沙发",
      "from": 299.47,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 105,
      "to": 301.01
    },
    {
      "content": "我们希望这个不存在",
      "from": 301.01,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 106,
      "to": 302.9
    },
    {
      "content": "现在",
      "from": 302.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 107,
      "to": 303.34
    },
    {
